ContentDesc_Porta Decumana: Making your way through the Praetorium, you sweep aside wave after wave of defenders before finally coming face-to-face with Gaius van Baelsar himself. Unable to overcome you by his own hands, the Black Wolf takes control of the Ultima Weapon and sets upon you once more. Do what you have come to do, and see that the magitek monstrosity never threatens Eorzea again.
Instancecontenttextdata_33200_Text: The Ultima Weapon has partaken of the power of eikons! None can stand against it!
Instancecontenttextdata_33202_Text: The wind is at my beck and call!
Instancecontenttextdata_33203_Text: Naught can pierce the raging tempest!
Instancecontenttextdata_33204_Text: Thy foe is Darkness clad in steel. If thou wouldst triumph, thou must look to the Light.
Instancecontenttextdata_33205_Text: Titan's essence...torn from the Ultima Weapon!?
Instancecontenttextdata_33206_Text: No matter─it still harbors the might of other eikons!
Instancecontenttextdata_33208_Text: The land itself is mine to wield!
Instancecontenttextdata_33210_Text: Once more, crystal bearer. Look to the Light to vanquish the Darkness.
Instancecontenttextdata_33212_Text: But the Ultima Weapon is not spent of eikon power yet!
Instancecontenttextdata_33214_Text: So this is the strength of the eikon-slayer...
Instancecontenttextdata_33215_Text: Very well, let us see how you fare when the Ultima Weapon's power inhibitor is disengaged!
Instancecontenttextdata_33216_Text: Naught will remain of you but ash!
Instancecontenttextdata_33217_Text: Yield not to the Darkness, my child. Pray to the Crystal with all thy being.
Instancecontenttextdata_33218_Text: No! How...how are you doing this!?
Instancecontenttextdata_33219_Text: We settle this once and for all!
Instancecontenttextdata_33220_Text: I need not the power of eikons to defeat you! Gaze upon true power!
Instancecontenttextdata_33221_Text: This is most...unexpected. You are possessed of great might, this I will allow.
Instancecontenttextdata_33222_Text: Yet yours is not the might of a ruler! Such is the difference between us─a difference that will assure my victory!
Instancecontenttextdata_33224_Text: How much destruction must be wreaked before you are sated!?
Instancecontenttextdata_33225_Text: I have not the strength...to shield thee again...
Instancecontenttextdata_33226_Text: Permit not the manifestation of that vile magick...lest Darkness prevail!
